[Student "S"]
{Compare this to Deal 10.

SOUTH has the strength for a raise to game in \Ss, but this could be dangerous since NORTH 
has overcalled rather than opened. Instead, SOUTH shows her strength with a Support Cue-bid.

NORTH has very minimal overcall so he just bids 2\S which SOUTH passes.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
[Deal "E:8.AKT87.KQJ4.AK6 K432.62.976.T752 Q75.QJ93.AT82.Q8 AJT96.54.53.J943"]
[Declarer "E"]
[Contract "6H"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "E"]
