[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/negative_doubles"]
[Student "S"]
{EAST has a maximum 1\H opening bid.

WEST would have made a Limit Raise in \Hs, but after SOUTH's overcall she 
makes a Support Cue-bid instead.

EAST thinks there may be a slam and bids 4NT Blackwood to check for Aces. When WEST admits to one Ace 
EAST bids the slam.}

